items.name: Import Services
items.description: Let us help you migrate your existing content onto Docsie seamlessly! Leverage our secure and straightforward migration process to preserve your hard work and take advantage of our innovative platform for enhanced knowledge sharing and collaboration.

items.name: Training
items.description: Accelerate your learning curve and mastery of Docsie with dedicated training packages designed specifically for your team's unique requirements and goals.

items.name: Support Package
items.description: Unlock full potential of your Docsie experience with dedicated support package. Receive personalized attention and guidance from experts, accelerating your progress and maximizing productivity.

items.name: Tenant Setup fee
items.description: Get personalized support for setting up your own private tenant environment exclusively managed by Docsie professionals. This includes customization of settings, installation of necessary plugins and integrations, and thorough testing to ensure smooth operation.

items.name: Configuration support
items.description: Enhance your Docsie knowledge base experience with dedicated configuration support for optimal organization, management, and retrieval of critical information

items.name: Business
items.description: Docsie Business Tier Subscription

items.name: Startup
items.description: Forever free. Forget about monthly payments.

items.name: Generative AI Actions
items.description: Harness the power of artificial intelligence to revolutionize your writing workflow. Our innovative AI-powered features will guide you every step of the way, from generating ideas and creating outlines to suggesting edits and proofreading your work. Save time and effort while producing high-quality content like never before.

items.name: Dedicated Training
items.description: Accelerate your learning curve and mastery of Docsie with dedicated training packages designed specifically for your team's unique requirements and goals.

items.name: Docsie API
items.description: Access powerful Docsie functionalities programmatically using our robust Public API and unlock new possibilities for automation and integration with other tools and systems.

items.name: Speech to Documentation
items.description: Speak your content into existence! Our browser-based voice recognition technology allows you to effortlessly dictate articles directly in your web browser. Say goodbye to typing fatigue and hello to hands-free creation.

items.name: Video to Documentation
items.description: Convert written knowledge bases into engaging visual content with ease. Utilize cutting-edge AI technology to transform textual support articles into dynamic videos, making complex topics more accessible and memorable to users.

items.name: Documentation To Video
items.description: Transform your videos into informative articles with ease using our advanced AI technology. Seamlessly import and upload video files directly from your device or cloud storage, then watch as our intelligent algorithms generate summaries and highlight key points automatically.

items.name: Chatbot Sessions
items.description: Increase engagement and streamline communication with additional chatbot sessions.

items.name: In-App Help Deployments - Per Help Center
Chatbot Deployments
items.description: Boost your online presence and customer outreach with expanded chatbot deployments

items.name: Workspaces
items.description: Manage multiple projects and teams efficiently with separate workspaces. Divide your organization into distinct departments or collaborators for optimal productivity and accountability.

items.name: Version
items.description: Expand your document version control capabilities with this handy upgrade. Purchase extra versions for greater flexibility in tracking changes and maintaining multiple iterations of your valuable documentation.

items.name: Chat Bot Consumers - Not Authenticated
items.description: Boost your business efficiency and customer experience with additional chatbot users. Streamline communication flows, reduce response times, and improve overall satisfaction rates through personalized interactions and automated support.

items.name: Chat Bot Consumers - Authenticated
items.description: Increase engagement and enhance communication channels with authenticated chatbots. Empower your customers or employees with direct lines of contact, enabling faster response times and improved customer service experiences.

items.name: Chat Bot Admin Users
items.description: Upgrade your chatbot administration capabilities with additional seats. Manage user interactions, respond to queries, and monitor analytics more efficiently with advanced administrative features and higher seat capacity.

items.name: Published Deployment Viewers (with Authentication)
items.description: Users who are viewing the deployments but need to be authenticated or named users
